        <item>
            <title>重现 iPhone 静音开关，新 USB-C 接口配件成减压神器</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/11/iphone-18/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-18</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/11/iphone-18/mobile-phone/phone-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[毛]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 10:03:04 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手机配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone 15 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1203663</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 在新推出的 iPhone 15 Pro 及 iPhone 15 Pro Max 系列中取消了过往的静音开关，改为全新的「动作」按钮。取消拨动设计后令许多用户感到不习惯，有外国设计师最近设法将静音开关重现到新系列 iPhone 当中。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1203706" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.38.11-PM-694x519.png" alt="" width="694" height="519" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.38.11-PM-694x519.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.38.11-PM-1204x900.png 1204w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.38.11-PM-768x574.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.38.11-PM.png 1372w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>外国设计师 Voicu Apostol 在设计网站 Dribbble 中发布一项设计，将本来在 iPhone 左侧的静音开关以 USB-C 接口手机配件的模式重新出现。 Voicu Apostol 表示，借此新系列 iPhone 的用家就可以直接将手机静音，而无需长按「动作」按钮方能静音。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1203705" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.43.51-PM-694x515.png" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.43.51-PM-694x515.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.43.51-PM-1212x900.png 1212w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.43.51-PM-768x570.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.43.51-PM.png 1374w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Voicu Apostol 又制作了一段影片模拟该静音开关配件的运作方式，并配上拨动期间的音效，意外地令片段变得非常疗愈。Voicu Apostol 又开玩笑指，该静音开关配件除了让用户可以安心睡眠外，更可以减少过度活跃症 ADHD 的症状。<img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1203708" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.54.05-PM-694x520.png" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.54.05-PM-694x520.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.54.05-PM-1201x900.png 1201w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.54.05-PM-768x575.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-09-at-2.54.05-PM.png 1372w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Voicu Apostol 在宣传图中提到该配件的价格为 $312.99 美元（约为港币 $2444 元），亦在文末提到相信读者会享受本片文章的幽默。这则文章很大可能只是一篇针对 iPhone 15 Pro 及 iPhone 15 Pro Max 系列的玩笑，最终并不会进行开发。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://dribbble.com/shots/22872687-Mute-Switch-Dongle">Dribbble</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

